Sukiyaki Western Django is definitely not a prequel to this though. I wouldn't even say it's even loosely based on it. It's more like Takashi Miike's japanese tribute to the spaghetti western. Storywise Sukiyaki has a lot more in common with A Fistfull of Dollars/Yojimbo than Django. A great movie in it's own right but it doesn't borrow a lot from Django besides the name.
